description.narrative: The program comprises (i) a program cluster approach for the Second Financial Sector Program Cluster (FSP II) comprising four subprograms for an aggregate amount not exceeding $40 million equivalent; (ii) a program loan of $10 million equivalent for subprogram 1, and (iii) a technical assistance (TA) grant for $1.7 million. The four subprograms will be implemented back-to-back with each succeeding subprogram to be processed sequentially upon completion of the preceding subprogram.
